  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>It’s time for your starring role in Deep Cuts.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on the role of Elise Weber, co-founder of film production studio Lights Camera Faction, as they embark on a blockbuster quest to save their best friend and creative partner by venturing through the duo’s expansive film catalog. Relive all of LCF’s iconic and cinematic moments as you gain superpowers and face off against a maniacal group of deprecated and deadly cartoon characters – The Learning Lads.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035010/extras/a7cec42e3e7fa0def0f5fd861c4dd9fc.poster.avif?t=1755251899\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035010/extras/a7cec42e3e7fa0def0f5fd861c4dd9fc.webm?t=1755251899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035010/extras/a7cec42e3e7fa0def0f5fd861c4dd9fc.mp4?t=1755251899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Physics Action! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kinetically driven and dynamically interactive melee and firearms combat with diverse weapon options inside highly responsive environments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035010/extras/59d405119288b2d4f992130ffab41ec7.poster.avif?t=1755251899\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035010/extras/59d405119288b2d4f992130ffab41ec7.webm?t=1755251899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035010/extras/59d405119288b2d4f992130ffab41ec7.mp4?t=1755251899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Deep Lore and Environmental Storytelling! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the rich backstory of LCF and their hidden secrets as you journey through beloved movie genres and tropes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035010/extras/f05610e045ca55bc4a38c54534769675.poster.avif?t=1755251899\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035010/extras/f05610e045ca55bc4a38c54534769675.webm?t=1755251899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035010/extras/f05610e045ca55bc4a38c54534769675.mp4?t=1755251899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Neurareel Film Experiences! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in real-time scenes within living movie sets, mixing life and art in ways previously unexplored. Dive into various film genres from 1980s Horror and Retrofuturistic Sci-fi to Spaghetti Western and Film Noir as you take on the roles of different protagonists.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035010/extras/587425dec1811c6033243a5fcf3c1196.poster.avif?t=1755251899\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035010/extras/587425dec1811c6033243a5fcf3c1196.webm?t=1755251899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035010/extras/587425dec1811c6033243a5fcf3c1196.mp4?t=1755251899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Time Manipulation Abilities! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Harness cinematic augmentations, granting editing actions on the fly that make you the director. Use these abilities strategically to overcome obstacles, solve puzzles, and enemy barrages.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>It’s time for your starring role in Deep Cuts.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on the role of Elise Weber, co-founder of film production studio Lights Camera Faction, as they embark on a blockbuster quest to save their best friend and creative partner by venturing through the duo’s expansive film catalog. Relive all of LCF’s iconic and cinematic moments as you gain superpowers and face off against a maniacal group of deprecated and deadly cartoon characters – The Learning Lads.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035010/extras/a7cec42e3e7fa0def0f5fd861c4dd9fc.poster.avif?t=1755251899\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035010/extras/a7cec42e3e7fa0def0f5fd861c4dd9fc.webm?t=1755251899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035010/extras/a7cec42e3e7fa0def0f5fd861c4dd9fc.mp4?t=1755251899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Physics Action! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kinetically driven and dynamically interactive melee and firearms combat with diverse weapon options inside highly responsive environments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035010/extras/59d405119288b2d4f992130ffab41ec7.poster.avif?t=1755251899\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035010/extras/59d405119288b2d4f992130ffab41ec7.webm?t=1755251899\" ty