deo/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3035010/extras/587425dec1811c6033243a5fcf3c1196.mp4?t=1755251899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Time Manipulation Abilities! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Harness cinematic augmentations, granting editing actions on the fly that make you the director. Use these abilities strategically to overcome obstacles, solve puzzles, and enemy barrages.</p>",
